39:14.786 --> 39:15.787
Well, then she's an idiot.

39:15.821 --> 39:17.122
(giggles)

39:18.457 --> 39:20.091
(both moaning)

39:20.125 --> 39:21.727
Oh, Bob...

39:21.760 --> 39:24.162
(laughs)
I'm kidding,
I'm kidding, I'm kidding.

39:24.195 --> 39:25.764
It's Jim, right?
(laughs): Yeah.

39:25.797 --> 39:26.832
LUISA:
This is Mark.

39:30.869 --> 39:32.704
You see Mark, right?

39:32.738 --> 39:35.106
Yes.

39:35.140 --> 39:36.942
What are you doing here?

39:36.975 --> 39:42.614
I'm checking myself
into a psychiatric hospital.

39:42.648 --> 39:45.484
Or a wellness center
if you believe the brochure.

39:45.517 --> 39:46.952
*

39:46.985 --> 39:49.555
I can't go down this path again.

39:51.590 --> 39:55.527
Well, I'm... really glad
that you're getting help.

39:55.561 --> 39:57.896
After everything
that's happened,

39:57.929 --> 40:01.132
the fact that...

40:01.166 --> 40:04.002
you're still looking out
for me, it...

40:07.172 --> 40:09.575
Thank you.

40:09.608 --> 40:12.143
And you can have
your hotel shares back.

40:12.177 --> 40:13.545
What?

40:14.946 --> 40:16.815
That's not why I helped you.

40:16.848 --> 40:18.950
I know.

40:18.984 --> 40:21.419
That's why I'm giving them back.

40:33.098 --> 40:34.065
Hey, you.

40:34.099 --> 40:37.736
Everything okay?

40:37.769 --> 40:38.837
Yeah.

40:38.870 --> 40:39.838
(sighs)

40:43.208 --> 40:44.810
Luisa's going to get help.

40:44.843 --> 40:47.178
That's great.

40:47.212 --> 40:50.616
And she's giving me back
my hotel shares.

40:52.651 --> 40:54.019
What?
Yeah.

40:54.052 --> 40:56.187
She's giving everything back.

40:58.023 --> 40:59.725
See?

40:59.758 --> 41:02.628
You do the right thing
and good things happen.

41:02.661 --> 41:03.962
(laughs softly)

41:03.995 --> 41:05.196
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Oh, Jane,

41:05.230 --> 41:07.165
after all your
telenovela watching,

41:07.198 --> 41:09.935
you should know by now,
that's not true.

41:09.968 --> 41:12.103
I know it's not how you
wanted to get the hotel back,

41:12.137 --> 41:14.973
but it's still a good thing.

41:15.006 --> 41:16.274
My sister signed this
last night.

41:16.307 --> 41:19.711
All the shares
are now back in my name.

41:19.745 --> 41:23.148
Oh, well, unfortunately, due
to your sister's mental state,

41:23.181 --> 41:25.817
she's not allowed to change
any contractual agreement.

41:25.851 --> 41:27.653
What does that mean?
It reverts

41:27.686 --> 41:29.621
to the original agreement
she signed six weeks ago,

41:29.655 --> 41:32.558
which stated in the event
of her incapacitation,

41:32.591 --> 41:33.859
all her hotel
shares go to...

41:33.892 --> 41:36.027
I am new owner of Marbella!

41:36.061 --> 41:38.196
Good job, Anton.

41:40.732 --> 41:43.535
We did it.

41:43.569 --> 41:45.270
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
I did tell you

41:45.303 --> 41:47.505
there would be some
very fine acting.
